reviewText: Are you serious?? I kept waiting for something meaningful to happen. Just a group of brainless twits on a road trip un-prepared. I don't know how it got so many good reviews.. Waste of time and money...

expect a different type of film played out like a home video. Its not bad acting, just true to real life which is the appeal of the movie. It has similarities to the blairwitch project. Reminds me of the type of people I didn't want to hang out with when I was young. FYI: the actors also produced, wrote and directed the film which is uber cool.
The movie was boring. I almost fell asleep while waiting for something to happen. The acting was awful. Don't waste your money.

I loved this movie from beginning to end.  It was filled with adventure, suspense and thrills along the wild ride of which is a fight for survival.  So if you are looking for a good movie that will leave an imprint then choose this one... wow.
I laughed, I cried, I had nightmares after watching what was a very realistic movie about 6 young adults on "vacation". I highly recommend this buy!
